sentences.english: Unfortunately, we cannot send other Test Report forms to you directly.
sentences.chinese: 但是，我們不能將額外的成績單直接寄給您本人。

sentences.english: What happens if a candidate loses their Test Report Form?
sentences.chinese: 如果考生的成績單丟失怎麼辦？

sentences.english: After United Arab Republic three, gave 12 point 4 backboard report card, displayed not vulgarly .
sentences.chinese: 阿聯三節後繳出了12分4籃板的成績單，表現不俗。

sentences.english: So they don't have to worry about things going on their transcript.
sentences.chinese: 所以他們不必擔心成績單。

sentences.english: Did you bring your transcript from high school?
sentences.chinese: 你高中的成績單帶來了嗎？

sentences.english: The candidates will received their Test Report Forms with one month after they finished their test.
sentences.chinese: 考生將在考試結束後一個月內收到成績單。

sentences.english: But the rude awakening soon came when I got my first set of grades.
sentences.chinese: 但在我拿到第一份成績單的時候，我猛醒了。

sentences.english: My duff transcript did not faze the schools I applied to.
sentences.chinese: 我那份改頭換面的成績單，並沒有引起商學院的疑慮。

sentences.english: Teach user with predefined transcript and from audio file.
sentences.chinese: 用戶預定義教成績單和音頻文件。

sentences.english: Meet to talk about your college plans and review your transcript.
sentences.chinese: 與她談你的選校計劃，並討論你的成績單。

sentences.english: A highschool transcript is needed when applying for universities.
sentences.chinese: 當申請入大學時是需要高中的成績單的。

sentences.english: His mother scowled at him when she saw his score report.
sentences.chinese: 看到他的成績單時，她母親一臉不悅地看着他。

sentences.english: One of the great tortures of life is receiving grades on papers and tests.
sentences.chinese: 生活中最折磨人的事情莫過於收取考試成績單。

sentences.english: And that means we’ll finally be able to issue a report card on the president’s arms-control agenda.
sentences.chinese: 公衆終於可以給奧巴馬發一份武器控制的成績單了。

sentences.english: Please fill in the highest TOEFL score obtained and provide us with photocopies of the results slips.
sentences.chinese: 請填寫獲取的最高託福測驗分數並提交成績單副本。

sentences.english: Please attach the two-sided copies of your student ID card and the school grades report.
sentences.chinese: 請附學生證正反面影本及歷年成績單于後。
